 World Cup|2001]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/u20worldcup/archive/argentina2001/teams/team=1888264/index.html|title=FIFA World Youth Championship Argentina 2001 - Teams - Ghana - Matches|website=FIFA.com|publisher=F\u00e9d\u00e9ration Internationale de Football Association|accessdate=11 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[UNFP Player of the Month|Ligue 1 Player of the Month]]: October 2004\n*[[Ligue 1 Player of the Year]]: 2004\u201305\n*[[Troph\u00e9es UNFP du football#Team of the Year|Ligue 1 Team of the Year]]: 2002\u201303, 2004\u201305\n*[[CAF Team of the Year]]: 2005, 2006, 2008, 2009\n*[[BBC African Footballer of the Year]]: 2006<ref>{{cite news |title=Essien wins BBC African award |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/6224665.stm |website=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=5 January 2007 |accessdate=17 August 2009 }}</ref>\n*[[Ghana Player of the Year]]: 2007\n*[[List of Chelsea F.C. players#Player of the Year|Chelsea Player of the Year]]: [[2006\u201307 Chelsea F.C. season|2006\u201307]]<ref name=\"Player of the Year\"/>\n*[[List of Chelsea F.C. players#Goal of the Year|Chelsea Goal of the Year]]: 2006\u201307 vs Arsenal,<ref name=\"Player of the Year\">{{cite web|url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/2363410 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130425091228/http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/2363410 |url-status=dead |archive-date=25 April 2013 |title=Cech Wins the Big One |date=19 May 2011 |accessdate=25 June 2014 |publisher=Chelsea FC |work=chelseafc.com }}</ref> 2008\u201309 vs Barcelona<ref name=\"Player of the Year\"/>\n*[[2008 Africa Cup of Nations#Awards|2008 Africa Cup of Nations]]: Team of the Tournament<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.modernghana.com/news2/158365/2/le-roy-attacks-caf-on-nations-cup-all-star-team.html |title=Le Roy Attacks CAF on Nations Cup All-Star Team |date=22 February 2008 |accessdate=21 January 2013|work=ModernGhana.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{