.uk/sport2/hi/football/africa/6224665.stm |website=BBC Sport |publisher=British Broadcasting Corporation |date=5 January 2007 |accessdate=17 August 2009 }}</ref>\n*[[Ghana Player of the Year]]: 2007\n*[[List of Chelsea F.C. players#Player of the Year|Chelsea Player of the Year]]: [[2006\u201307 Chelsea F.C. season|2006\u201307]]<ref name=\"Player of the Year\"/>\n*[[List of Chelsea F.C. players#Goal of the Year|Chelsea Goal of the Year]]: 2006\u201307 vs Arsenal,<ref name=\"Player of the Year\">{{cite web|url=http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/2363410 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130425091228/http://www.chelseafc.com/news-article/article/2363410 |url-status=dead |archive-date=25 April 2013 |title=Cech Wins the Big One |date=19 May 2011 |accessdate=25 June 2014 |publisher=Chelsea FC |work=chelseafc.com }}</ref> 2008\u201309 vs Barcelona<ref name=\"Player of the Year\"/>\n*[[2008 Africa Cup of Nations#Awards|2008 Africa Cup of Nations]]: Team of the Tournament<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.modernghana.com/news2/158365/2/le-roy-attacks-caf-on-nations-cup-all-star-team.html |title=Le Roy Attacks CAF on Nations Cup All-Star Team |date=22 February 2008 |accessdate=21 January 2013|work=ModernGhana.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n* {{Official website|http://www.michaelessiengh.com/home.html}}\n* [http://www.premierleague.com/en-gb/players/profile.overview.html/michael-essien Premier League Profile]\n* {{Webarchive |url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131205221146/http://www.chelseafc.com/first-team/player/27901 |title=Chelsea F.C. Profile (chelseafc.com) }}\n* {{ESPN FC|9799<!-- /michael-essien -->}}\n* {{FIFA|175524}}\n\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Ghana squads\n| bg = #CA1118\n| fg = #FBE816\n| bordercolor = black\n| list1  = \n{{Ghana squad 2002 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n{{Ghana squad 2006 FIFA World Cup}}\n{{Ghana squad 2008 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n{{Ghana squad 2010 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n{{Ghana squad 2014 FIFA World Cup}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes\n| title = Awards\n| bg = gold\n| fg = navy\n| bordercolor = black\n| list1 = \n{{2002\u201303 Ligue 1 UNFP Team of the Year}}\n{{2004\u201305 Ligue 1 UNFP Team of the Year}}\n{{Ghanaian Footballer of the Year}}\n{{BBC African Footballer of the Year}}\n{{Chelsea F.C. Player of the Year}}\n{{Ligue 1 Player of the Year}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Essien, Michael}}\n[[Category:1982 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Fante people]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian Roman Catholics]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Accra]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Association football utility players]]\n[[Category:St. Augustine's College alumni]]\n[[Category:Liberty Professionals F.C. players]]\n[[Category:SC Bastia players]]\n[[Category:Olympique Lyonnais players]]\n[[Category:Chelsea F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Real Madrid CF players]]\n[[Category:A.C. Milan players]]\n[[Category:Panathinaikos F.C. players]]\n[[Category:Persib Bandung players]]\n[[Category:Sabail FK players]]\n[[Category:Ligue 1 players]]\n[[Category:Premier League players]]\n[[Category:La Liga players]]\n[[Category:Serie A players]]\n[[Category:Super League Greece players]]\n[[Category:Liga 1 (Indonesia) players]]\n[[Category:Azerbaijan Premier League players]]\n[[Category:UEFA Champions League winning players]]\n[[Category:Ghana under-20 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Ghana international footballers]]\n[[Category:2002 African Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:2006 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:2008 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:2010 Africa Cup of Nations players]]\n[[Category:2014 FIFA World Cup players]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian expatriate footballers]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian expatriate sportspeople in France]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian expatriate sportspeople in England]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian expatriate sportspeople in Spain]]\n[[Category:Ghanaian expatriate sportspeople i